Some Standard Commands, there are plenty of others....

Moving Around
N E S W U D    GO      JUMP   LOOK    EXITS          
Items
GET     DROP    WEAR   REMOVE GIVE    STEAL    INVENTORY      PUT     UNLOCK
EXAMINE VALUE   LIGHT  EXTINGUISH     TURN     OPEN           CLOSE   LOCK
EAT     PRESS   PUSH   DRINK	      EMPTY
Talking
SHOUT   SAY    TELL    
Informational
WHO     HELP   LEVELS  
Utility 
QUIT    SAVE   SCORE   BRIEF  CONVERSE         LOG     
Combat
WEAPON  KILL   <WITH WEAPON> to select weapon  FLEE
Atmosphere
LAUGH   CRY    BURP    HICCUP SLAP    TICKLE   KISS    SCREAM BOUNCE  STARE
